event CreateGame(address indexed gameAddress, address indexed ownerAddress)
event RoleAdminChanged(bytes32 indexed role, bytes32 indexed previousAdminRole, bytes32 indexed newAdminRole)
event RoleGranted(bytes32 indexed role, address indexed account, address indexed sender)
event RoleRevoked(bytes32 indexed role, address indexed account, address indexed sender)

function create(address gameAddress, tuple(address ownerAddress, string name, string author, string renderer, string avatarFilter, string itemFilter, string gemFilter, string website, uint8 status) game)

function gameByAddress(address gameAddress) view returns (tuple(address ownerAddress, string name, string author, string renderer, string avatarFilter, string itemFilter, string gemFilter, string website, uint256 createdAt, uint256 updatedAt, uint8 status) game)

function gameByIndex(uint256 index) view returns (address gameAddress, tuple(address ownerAddress, string name, string author, string renderer, string avatarFilter, string itemFilter, string gemFilter, string website, uint256 createdAt, uint256 updatedAt, uint8 status) game)
function getRoleMember(bytes32 role, uint256 index) view returns (address)
function hasRole(bytes32 role, address account) view returns (bool)

function update(address gameAddress, tuple(address ownerAddress, string name, string author, string renderer, string avatarFilter, string itemFilter, string gemFilter, string website, uint8 status) game)
